anscripts & Records Grades Exams Graduation & Diplomas Transfer Articulation Community college course transfer guides Community college courses that apply to UNT degrees Talk to a Transfer counselor Visit Us Eagle Student Services Center Room 202 Mail Us Division of Enrollment University of North Texas 1155 Union Circle #311481 Denton TX 76203 Contact Us 940-565-4510 Technical issues? Site last updated on December 16, 2015 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on December 16, 2015 | Important Links 